{
  "_comment": "Two distinct BatteryPass sources are referenced separately. (1) samm-* = the BatteryPass Consortium SAMM aspect models (github.com/batterypass/BatteryPassDataModel), real published versions 1.2.0 (Performance 1.2.1); these match the skos mappings in battery.ttl. (2) bpr: = the GEFEG BatteryPass-Ready longlist v1.3 (thebatterypass.eu / batterypass-ready.gefeg.com), which publishes no RDF IRIs, so this is an OpenEPCIS-hosted reference namespace for its longlist-only attributes (the DPP-information group #1-#4). There is no SAMM 1.3.0 and no SAMM DPPInformation submodel.",
